data.description: GATED SUBDIVISION, great location in a secluded neighborhood. This beauty has so much space for big family, guests, and entertaining.  In addition to the family living area with fireplace, large dining area and formal dining room, you will enjoy an Office,  Large game room with Bar, Kitchenette, TV, Ping Pong, Card games and French doors leading to an outdoor Patio and beautiful back yard.  Also plenty of other outdoor spaces with porches and decks. Innovative Gemstone lighting, by LiveWire, has been installed for vibrant, color-changing display for any Holiday. Close to major highways, shopping and downtown. This is a must see.
